{"tid":203884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"母產下雙胞胎後離世　送行者讓人淚崩","createTime":"2017-04-16T15:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T17:02:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"051b8f7b93006e7c9435d024dad66a94ee480cbe","tid":203884,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170416/420_e068c6454e66b4b196168f23edeb0a75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170416%2F420_e068c6454e66b4b196168f23edeb0a75.jpg&h=fbb7695f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>禮儀師許伊妃常在臉書分享工作點滴，她昨晚上傳一張抱著新生兒的照片，並po文「這應該是我遇到最小的家屬了」</strong></span>，她提到，產下雙胞胎的媽媽，只跟孩子相處4小時就過世了，感嘆：「每個孩子，都是女人用性命去拼博來的。」<br />\n許伊妃在臉書po文說，嬰兒出生第10天，家裡沒人可以照顧，「為爸爸一個人要料理所有的事物，還沒滿月的嬰兒也只能帶來殯儀館。」<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>她說，生下雙胞胎的產婦，跟孩子相處只有短短4個小時，妹妹還在保溫箱</strong></span>，「媽媽連抱都沒有抱到就離世了」。<br />\n亡者丈夫說，孩子在家不停哭鬧，但車子一開到會館門口，哭聲就停了！「在媽媽靈前才睡的安穩..你信嗎？嗯我相信！！」她感嘆，「媽媽真的很辛苦，生命真的很脆弱；人生也是真的很無常。」<br />\n「看到這裡，快跟你媽媽說聲辛苦了，男人更應該轉身抱抱你老婆並說聲您真偉大.....若你身為婆婆，也更應該好好疼惜別人家的女兒...每個孩子，都是女人用性命去拼博來的。」<br />\n許多網友不捨：「加油」、「加油。孩子的爸爸。」、「媽媽真的好偉大，baby要健康平安長大」、「孩子的爸要堅強，小寶寶要健康長大喔，媽媽真的是無比偉大啊！」、「請你要加油&hellip;為了小孩要堅持堅強下去&hellip;加油！」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170416/1098925/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170416%2F1098925%2F&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7e2f85b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170416/1098925/</a>"},{"pid":"cfa1579ee41ee213fb9b11c86d6874c513af7537","tid":203884,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5416b96fcb39a8c9ca8687efd3ee9a86e85bfd5","tid":203884,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:39:36.000Z","msg":"母親節快到又吹奏"},{"pid":"1845ab130d46b255e0c80124e3abc406885e049a","tid":203884,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751f05fdbfc636778edc42005bad7ca509f19aa5","tid":203884,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}